lemma compress_normalize_output_interfaces_preserves_normalized_n_primitive: "normalized_n_primitive (disc, sel) P m \<Longrightarrow> (\<forall>a. \<not> disc (OIface a)) \<Longrightarrow> normalized_nnf_match m \<Longrightarrow> compress_normalize_output_interfaces m = Some m' \<Longrightarrow> normalized_nnf_match m' \<and> normalized_n_primitive (disc, sel) P m'"
